name: Jason R. Koivu
text: On the blessedly rare occasion I find myself at Kmart I have, even more rarely, grabbed some "pizza" at the Little Caesars harbored within. The place is always a mess. I'm not sure which is greasier, the pizza or the tables. If you're …More

name: Kristen Wilson
text: Tables and floor are disgustingly dirty. Service is slow. Employees don’t acknowledge you if you are standing at the counter. With all the employees they have on staff I’m confused as to why not one of them takes the time to wipe the tables, sweep the floor or take out the overfilled trash.

name: Randi Priest
text: This place is awful. Everytime I come they never have hot and READY pizza. takes at least 20 mins for anything when they actually take your order.

name: Robert Buchanan
text: Poor service! Really slow. This location sucks.

name: Maria gutierrez
text:
